Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:34.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanae!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:37.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Here! For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:41.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... A love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:43.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course not! It's just a regular letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:45.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone's writing them to their friends these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Haven't you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:47.79,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.37,0:00:51.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry, Yukari,\NI'm gonna write one for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:54.29,Main,,0,0,0,,That's nice of you, just don't do it in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:55.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You need to focus on the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:58.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Friendship is way more important than any lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.91,Main,,0,0,0,,What, are the girls all suddenly\Ninto writing letters now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:03.45,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:05.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if some of them are writing love letters, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:09.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe. They do seem really into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:10.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:12.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Love letters, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:14.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't get the appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.25,0:01:15.91,Main,,0,0,0,,They could just say what they want out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:17.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Why bother to write it all down?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:19.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Must have a lotta time on their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:29.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:31.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanae, you're going a little overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:33.50,Main,,0,0,0,,One kick was enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,So kicking him at all's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:39.70,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, let's start class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:42.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Open up your textbooks to page seventy-six.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:49.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Takagi's writing letters, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:55.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I forget that she's just your ordinary girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:12.66,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:53.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong, Nishikata?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.33,Main,,0,0,0,,No, nothing, everything's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:03:59.58,Main,,0,0,0,,A letter? Who's it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:01.08,Main,,0,0,0,,And why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:03.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if some of them are writing love letters, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:06.29,Main,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, that's obviously not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone's playing a prank on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:09.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:13.91,Main,,0,0,0,,This could be Takagi's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.62,Main,,0,0,0,,No, it's gotta be her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:19.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Takagi--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:20.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:22.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Reign it in, Nishikata!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:24.50,Main,,0,0,0,,What if it's somebody else? What if it isn't Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.86,Main,,0,0,0,,If she finds out I got a letter,\Nshe'll just use that to tease me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:30.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:31.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:41.04,Main,,0,0,0,,It's nice out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:42.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you hiding something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:45.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would I be hiding something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:50.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Dunno. But you're suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:51.70,Main,,0,0,0,,And blushing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:54.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You're just imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:56.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.29,Main,,0,0,0,,But why is your textbook closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Well. You see, I uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:03.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet it's why your face is red.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:06.16,Main,,0,0,0,,No, it's not! And my face is not red!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:08.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure nothing's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's why I said so!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:16.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I was imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.98,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, that letter in your textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:22.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I put that there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:26.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:31.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:34.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, duh. It was obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:36.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:38.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:41.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I was just having fun making you squirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:43.37,Main,,0,0,0,,So. You gonna read what's inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:45.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You wrote something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:46.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it is a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.95,Main,,0,0,0,,You're just messing with me like always, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you saying something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:59.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll read it at home later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Read it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:05.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:09.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Because. School's over after this period.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.16,Main,,0,0,0,,And I wanted an answer by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:12.66,Main,,0,0,0,,An answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:20.16,Main,,0,0,0,,If it's a letter that needs an answer,\Nthen it's a letter asking a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:22.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Does that mean it's not just meant to mess with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:26.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if some of them are writing love letters, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,What if Takao's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:29.95,Main,,0,0,0,,What if it's a love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:31.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:37.15,Main,,0,0,0,,By any chance, would this happen\Nto be a love letter, or...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:41.93,Main,,0,0,0,,What's with the silence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:46.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, I will, just gimme a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:48.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I gotta open it up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:50.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Based on that reaction,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:53.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd wager anything that this\Nis designed just to tease me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:55.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Whatever it ends up saying, I have to be firm
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.33,Main,,0,0,0,,and confident so that she doesn't get the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:59.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Be bold! Be brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.36,Main,,0,0,0,,But what if...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:04.00,Main,,0,0,0,,No, it can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:05.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.53,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:12.33,Main,,0,0,0,,But if it is a love letter, then... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:37.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You could have just asked me to my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.94,Main,,0,0,0,,But everyone's writing letters now. It's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,However, I was also curious how you'd react.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:51.14,Main,,0,0,0,,So I was right! You were messing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut it, Nishikata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:18.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:20.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome. I gotta go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:25.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, one second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:28.58,Main,,0,0,0,,What's your name, new kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Did I forget to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:32.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:36.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishikata. Congrats on getting in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:41.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:47.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll all be learning alongside each\Nother over the course of the next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna force you to get along with everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:53.04,Main,,0,0,0,,But I hope you realize you're only gonna\Nmake the experience worse if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:56.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, did I lose it somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:09:00.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't want to bore you right\Noff the bat with a long speech, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Slept in on the first day?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:06.12,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I was, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:08.37,Main,,0,0,0,,If nothing else, I admire your audacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:09.95,Main,,0,0,0,,But... Sir, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:11.12,Main,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:13.97,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:16.62,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, then. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:27.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, great, Everyone's staring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:29.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to make friends with people and clear things up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.75,Main,,0,0,0,,before I become known as "that\Nguy who was late on day one."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:37.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tanabe, a moment of your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:42.25,Main,,0,0,0,,They called and said they're running a little bit late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:43.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Are we pushing the entrance ceremony back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:46.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll keep you posted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:51.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I just got word that the entrance\Nceremony is running behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:53.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Sounds like it's gonna take a\Nwhile before they're all set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:56.12,Main,,0,0,0,,So in the meantime...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:57.62,Main,,0,0,0,,...we're figuring out seating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:05.77,Main,,0,0,0,,At least I'm not in the front. Sucks to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:06.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:10.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm literally as far in the corner as I possibly can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Normally I'd be happy about being\Nthis far away from the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:16.25,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the best spot to goof off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:18.05,Main,,0,0,0,,But I don't know anyone as it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:20.77,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no one behind me or to my left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:23.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Worse, I'm sitting next to a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:27.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you actually sleep in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:29.87,Main,,0,0,0,,She's talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:32.79,Main,,0,0,0,,It looked like you were about\Nto say something to the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:34.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:37.00,Main,,0,0,0,,No. I didn't actually sleep in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:40.29,Main,,0,0,0,,If only I'd made it here earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I was at the school on time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:44.91,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Takagi's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoever that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.85,Main,,0,0,0,,All right everyone, head to the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:52.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:53.04,Main,,0,0,0,,And no running
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:57.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:00.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to walk there together?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:01.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:08.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:13.29,Main,,0,0,0,,You will soon be given a great gift, the right to vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:16.87,Main,,0,0,0,,With it, you will choose students\Nfor positions of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:21.45,Main,,0,0,0,,It's important you select politicians who\Nare worthy of your trust and confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:25.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Similarly, your mothers and fathers\Nchoose their representatives by voting...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:31.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that speech crazy long?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:34.33,Main,,0,0,0,,That dude was talking so long I almost fell asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:37.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I know, it was like when we started elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:41.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You're pretty cool for coming' in late on the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:42.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:45.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Everybody quit yapping' and take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for getting back late, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:00.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Just go sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:05.09,Main,,0,0,0,,That's it for today, but remember,\Nreal classes start tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:07.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't mess around because I'm letting you out early.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:09.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Go straight home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:11.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:15.92,Main,,0,0,0,,How 'bout I try to guess why you were late today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:17.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:21.12,Main,,0,0,0,,If I get it right on my first try, I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:26.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, how is she gonna figure it out on her first try?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:32.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You were delivering a lost item.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:33.33,Main,,0,0,0,,What? How'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:36.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey. Quiet down, Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:37.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:40.82,Main,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.45,Main,,0,0,0,,How indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:55.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:57.16,Main,,0,0,0,,You're Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:13:00.12,Main,,0,0,0,,You weren't here yet when\Neveryone introduced themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:11.54,Main,,0,0,0,,What's with that reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:12.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! I just said to be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:13.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:23.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot. For picking it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:29.41,Main,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.33,Main,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Seventy-two! Seventy-three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:48.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Seventy-four! Seventy-five!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:58.25,Main,,0,0,0,,All this work's finally starting' to pay off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:10.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:41.37,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:46.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Morning, Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:48.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning yourself, Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:55.23,Main,,0,0,0,,So, hey. Have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:58.29,Main,,0,0,0,,They're going to be changing where everyone sits today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Really? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:07.20,Main,,0,0,0,,During homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:09.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Homeroom? That's first period!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:24.12,Main,,0,0,0,,--Taka-- --Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:31.20,Main,,0,0,0,,First period, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:33.41,Main,,0,0,0,,That'll be kinda fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:34.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:39.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, we haven't had a\Nseating change in a while, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:48.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:50.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess there are always positives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:52.87,Main,,0,0,0,,But if I'm being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:55.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be next to you for a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:00.82,Main,,0,0,0,,She's just messing with me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:02.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I almost fell for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:22.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Does anyone still need a number? No?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:25.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Then move your desks according\Nto the layout on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:27.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What number did you draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Twenty-nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:32.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. The far back again, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:35.00,Main,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:38.02,Main,,0,0,0,,This time I'm front and center.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:39.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:43.60,Main,,0,0,0,,We're going to be pretty far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:45.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:52.50,Main,,0,0,0,,All right! Now you can sneak\Nme answers on all our tests!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:53.91,Main,,0,0,0,,What? That's cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:55.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:56.33,Main,,0,0,0,,It's called mutual aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:57.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:58.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Well what do I get out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:00.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Words of encouragement from your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:01.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:03.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Yo, Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:04.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sitting' here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:06.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Nah, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:07.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,That's too bad. I was hoping we'd be closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:10.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:15.95,Main,,0,0,0,,My vision's been getting really bad lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:17.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope I can see what's on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm next to Nishikata, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:39.87,Main,,0,0,0,,You okay, Mano?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:42.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm just great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:47.10,Main,,0,0,0,,What's up? Are you not happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:50.81,Main,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. Feel free to just ignore me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:54.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm just depressed because I'm not sitting near Nakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:57.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I was really hoping we'd be next to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.04,Main,,0,0,0,,How far away is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:04.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:06.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyone! Please switch seats with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:14.16,Main,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to sneak an early lunch\Nif I'm right in front of the teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:17.16,Main,,0,0,0,,You aren't switching seats unless\Nyou have a legitimate reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Also, Kimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, do see me after class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:25.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Right in front of the teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:27.29,Main,,0,0,0,,But if I'm being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:29.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be next to you for a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:48.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kimura, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:50.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't see the board from here; let's switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:51.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:53.54,Main,,0,0,0,,But I already found someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:04.95,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:11.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishikata. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:22.41,Main,,0,0,0,,What the--?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:25.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess what? I'm sitting here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:26.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--? But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:29.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, first Nakai and Kimura switched.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:31.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Because Nakai couldn't see the board well enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:34.04,Main,,0,0,0,,So Nakai was all the way up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:38.33,Main,,0,0,0,,When she saw that, Mano wanted to switch with\Nme, since I was right next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:41.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Mano's short, so she prefers the front anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:43.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:46.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:49.16,Main,,0,0,0,,You tried to sit next to me up there, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:53.20,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:55.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see the board well from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:57.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:02.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:05.95,Main,,0,0,0,,What? It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:07.75,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, we're starting class.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:09.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Get your textbooks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:10.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. That reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:13.41,Main,,0,0,0,,What was it that you wanted to say earlier today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:15.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What, did I read you wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:17.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought you were looking for an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:26.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.13,Main,,0,0,0,,It took me a while to return this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:29.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:32.33,Main,,0,0,0,,From over summer break?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.66,Main,,0,0,0,,From then, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:36.89,Main,,0,0,0,,The first day of school?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:38.48,Main,,0,0,0,,You remembered that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:40.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course I did. You did too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:46.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Heh! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:49.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I made sure to wash it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:55.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:58.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm just kinda glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:01.00,Main,,0,0,0,,--Why? --Oh. Y'know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:02.02,Main,,0,0,0,,For a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:04.54,Main,,0,0,0,,That I got to return your handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:07.45,Main,,0,0,0,,And that we ended up next to each other again, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.62,Main,,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:10.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:12.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:15.29,Main,,0,0,0,,So here, we'd say, "I do not agree."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:18.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Or you could contract it to, "I don't agree."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:20.16,Main,,0,0,0,,That part's pretty easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:22.75,Main,,0,0,0,,But on the next page,\Nthings get a little more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:37.57,NOTE,,0,0,0,,"To Sanae-Chan"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:23.61,NOTE,,0,0,0,,"Dear Nishikata,\NLet's walk home together today. --Takagi"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:48.22,NOTE,,0,0,0,,"Dear Takagi-san, Thank you. --Nishikata"
